To run this Single Page Application,
install with npm all package and dependencies with
    *npm install*
in both folders webapp_Client and webapp_Server.
next, you need to run. mongo in this case we use mongod on cmd.
Run the server application with the command
    *nodemon app.js*
on webapp_Server
Run the Client server with the command
    *npm start*
on webapp_Client.

And in some browser put http://localhost:3001
